item.title: Shiawassee River Paddle Event - May 18 2008 - Holly to Fenton, Michigan
item.description: Shiawassee River Paddle Event Sunday, May 18, 2008 Start : WaterWorks Park in Holly, Michigan End : Strom Park in Fenton, Michigan Distance : 7 scenic miles of numerous twists and turns Canoe Rental available with Heavners Canoe Livery Schedule : 10:00 am : On-site registration begins WaterWorks Building, Broad Street 11:30 am : Introductory Ceremony North side WaterWorks Park 11:45 am : Experienced Canoeists Start at Millpond, Broad Street 12:15 pm : Novice/Youth Canoeists Start at Millpond, Broad Street 12:45 pm : Kayak/ Single person canoeists Start on Shiawassee River, Broad Street ** 1:15 pm : Leisure/fun paddle Start on Shiawassee River, Broad Street ** 6:00 pm : Final river sweep completed On-site availability of snacks and water.
